title: RiffTrax: Star Wars: The Force Awakens
writer: Conor Lastowka, Michael J. Nelson, Sean Thomason
actors: Bill Corbett, Kevin Murphy, Michael J. Nelson
plot: Scavenger girl Rey leaves her junkyard home to fulfill her destiny of escorting a robot around the galaxy. Mike Nelson, Bill Corbett, and Kevin Murphy are here to see if there's more to the story in this humorous commentary.
